The '''Orşova Wind Farm''' is an under construction [[wind power]] project in [[Mehedinţi County]], [[Romania]]. It will consist of an individual wind farm with 25 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.stirilocale.ro/Fonduri_germane_pentru_un_parc_eolian_IDN660974.html Fonduri germane pentru un parc eolian {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 1.4 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 35 MW of power, enough to power over 22,925 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$75 million.

